text.tspan: Excess mortality: Deaths from all causes compared to
The percentage difference between the reported number of weekly or monthly deaths in 2020–2023 and the average
number of deaths in the same period over the years 2015–2019. The reported number might not count all deaths
that occurred due to incomplete coverage and delays in reporting.
Data source: Human Mortality Database (2023); World Mortality Dataset (2023)
